summary: Green, redbrown and red maple woods around Riften
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://s25.postimg.cc/6pa05cojj/image.jpg[/img]
[img]https://s25.postimg.cc/xbr282i4f/image.jpg[/img]
[img]https://s25.postimg.cc/7u8noh0e7/aaa.jpg[/img]
[size=4]I always liked the red and green maples in TESIV Ovlivion so I decided to import them into Skyrim.
Replaces the yellow vanilla ashes around Riften with green, redbrown or red maples.
Changes leaves, bark, ground texture and distant lod. Also added retexture of leaves falling animation.[/size]

[size=3]Installation:
NMM or manual (unzip and copy/paste into Data/textures folder). Install only one file.
Uninstallation: remove the files.

Changelog:
1.0 Initial release
1.2 Added green and redbrown variant
1.3 Fixed distant lod issue
